"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"DAO represents Decentralized. Autonomous. Organization. Just like DAO in buddhism, which means the literal 'way' of Buddha, the return to the universal source, dharma and nirvana. Sounds too good?\\n\\nIn crypto world, DAO has equal idealistic purpose of real-decentralization approach to all projects, and it’s not being ruined by the authority associations just yet.\\n\\n> According to @VitaliKGod mentioned in a recent interview: “**I think DAOs are definitely going to be more important over time...that’s something I think we’ll see soon.”**\\n\\nThe concept of DAO is actually not complicated. It’s like a big machine and the mechanism is operate using smart contracts. Whenever there’re new opinions or decisions to be made, the members in that DAO vote for the decision moving forward. DAO tries to create an extreme democratic environment, on the good days.\\n\\nWhats’s the pros and cons of DAO in reality though?\\n\\nThe benefits of DAO:\\n\\n1. Equal voice to their members, who can vote for the result that could benefits everyone\\n2. High transparency, anyone can view the voting results\\n3. The entry level is easy, it helps recruiting global talents\\n4. Rules are made through smart contracts\\n5. Without a typical management structure or board of directors\\n\\nThe cons of DAO:\\n\\n1. In the event of serious disagreements, the organization may be split.\\n2. So far DAO are still belongs to different chains, so it’s not truly decentralized yet.\\n3. DAO has some legal agreements to be sorted with the authorities today.\\n\\nThere are different types of DAO like Protocol DAO, Venture DAO, NFT DAO and Social DAO. Here are the top ten DAO that worth to watch in 2022:\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/x1i1QqlJnafeqp714cY_V.png?height=1350&width=2400)\\n\\n\",\"timestamp\":1641974532,\"title\":\"Benefits of DAO? Get to know DAOs in 4.5 minutes read. \"},\"digest\":\"gtbl9c5Xx_B183SH2JjnTcHqEV8a55RtNaWXLnr-8_s\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x99B400fd7A047a52c3A7C95F5595eBe251AC8a99\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"b5ubyXf4U_PW8VDbOu7jDCa_8wT-Ex6_beAhEMhm6s4\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"JDvL-3fL1jERnWSsiUjoqrgR3ShYijmwSVby-YoAKwQ\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"2YiJWOtV1AqpTWY4EWrGrPCNrXyElTSQdehW96NcJ7cX4R_GUHu7HcPYZerTVBTtrEMjsvjTA_QGaxJFq-yVTg\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x66394baa3604e7d6b3fc643d825d4a571200dfb5f2884494fa83743c032efee47e55c6195d086a9383339c5c495bfad3fbd09ed39c521b09e4c754e2813698131b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"b5ubyXf4U_PW8VDbOu7jDCa_8wT-Ex6_beAhEMhm6s4\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"JDvL-3fL1jERnWSsiUjoqrgR3ShYijmwSVby-YoAKwQ\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"AbEl22_cDez3nPo5025-1W_sshaoT0gKv_CssGIsZaw\"}"